Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為追回GUNDAM2號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂向星海中進發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星之滄海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同在考驗這些年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那裏等待他們的是新的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年戰爭的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化做驚濤駭浪向浦木襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸損毀的GUNDAM1號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲響徹四方的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對處於困境的浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的心中確實捕捉到了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs60}馮·布朗的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再派一個人來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要到馮·布朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是體無完膚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿納海姆的人可要高興得流眼淚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿爾比昂沒被擊沉已是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托那傢伙的福嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰沉的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總算能得到上陸許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說增援是沒指望了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在聯邦軍的體質因保守而變得僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚們對迪拉茲艦隊的評價也太樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的權限無法再多調派艦隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等迪拉茲發難之後就太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮·布朗港灣管理局來電
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予第一區宇宙港的入港許可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘往香港於16:20起飛的班機佛羅伊德的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣真新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有妮娜小姐陪著的話就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混、混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐在工作啊，工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女如雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是妮娜的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了，很辛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴普爾頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安歸來比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是勞您操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟出動重力下用的機型去參加空間戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長下達的1號機的宇宙用換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及整修要趕在後天前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的要求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常務，我也要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將至今為止的數據連同報告書送到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明早要看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夜晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5907…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以米諾夫斯基粒子散佈的濃度就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，司考特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想想別的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了，西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有喝？宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地喝啊，盡情地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時登場的就是聯邦的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏大爺我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把迪拉茲艦隊的傢伙們抓了扔、抓了扔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那GUNDAM是你駕駛的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM被弄壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被菜鳥機師駕駛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會給阿納海姆添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹夜修理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好意思悠閒地喝酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是怕看到壞掉的GUNDAM會難受？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙、蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊？少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狼狽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺盛氣凌人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人也不打聲招呼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會把這兒當成地球了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是月球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是誰都要向聯邦搖尾乞憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，該我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說晚安還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MS機師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還、還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多鍛煉鍛煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會死在迪拉茲艦隊手上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點難度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你勤奮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不偶爾透透氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可會燃燒殆盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在為以前的事賭氣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再談個戀愛就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能使戀愛、工作兩不誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想嫁給GUNDAM嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請、請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有食慾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗把臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候大駕，來得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿納海姆也挺會做生意的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大主顧聯邦的船在第一港口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊卻是資源搬入港？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲，這事沒傳達給您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後得給我聯絡得徹底點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的補給艦入港時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再有聯邦軍嚴陣以待的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把殖民地扔到月球上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會銘記在心的，希瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人的話就別說「在下」！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天似乎有聯邦軍的艦隻入港
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯還要麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯準備我的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫宏·浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼逃出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕戰鬥了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都怪我才使MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣想的話就趁早的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那要是能行的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年戰爭時的MA？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}MA：Mobile All-Range Maneuverability Offence\NUtility Reinforcement(全領域泛用支援機動兵器)的縮寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西還能動的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是廢品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木仍舊沒有聯絡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個會添亂的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分這麼多層啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了下層的話可就棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最下層只有工廠和廢品店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不懂我的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子再不適可而止的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊基板過熱燒燬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得更換才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒錢僱人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請讓我在此多待幾天作為補償吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回船上去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在被說成逃兵之前，一直沒發覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，直說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這些部件就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會搞來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到宏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也毫無音信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉女士…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何時…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要幫敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒法修好凱利都快放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是聯邦軍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓他收留我一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是凱利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一年戰爭中失去了一隻手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此被撤離了MS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的鬥志還沒燃盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生曾是機師…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，請接入港聯邦軍的船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天入港的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於太空住民衷心企求自治權的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦行使其強大的軍事力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那萌芽扼殺在搖籃之中的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有足夠的事實來加以證明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架GUNDAM是以核攻擊為目的而開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架違反南極條約的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其存在本身便足以證明聯邦的險惡意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那麼軟弱的男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中更上等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏竟然有如此東西沉睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過以你的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在改造成單手也能操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是凱利·雷茲那大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西能參與星塵作戰的話就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪、迪拉茲艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過來得及嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的船明天出港
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕不上的話就無法參加作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明、明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些傢伙是迪拉茲艦隊的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你曾是ZION的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷聽可不禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可沒求你留下或修理MA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉女士也在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種窩囊廢沒資格批評我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心就放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就夾起尾巴快滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那樣，凱利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會成為喪家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩拉聯絡我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你似乎在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是忙於阿納海姆的工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不偶爾透透氣，會否燃燒殆盡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情好點了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回阿爾比昂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事沒做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深沉在心底揮之不去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你也轉告艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你特地來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的測試在阿納海姆的利巴莫工廠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午10點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回船上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憐憫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若就此不干機師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺弄機械來維持生計…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉就希望我那麼過一生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣當個廢品店老闆也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣干廢品店的工作，也會有某種…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這裏並不是自己歸宿的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心底深處會有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終究是個機師的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見時我們就是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那一拳很有力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏·浦木少尉現在返回執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.46,0:24:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.10,0:25:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM1號機-Full Burnern
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.49,0:25:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.70,0:28:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預    告
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.79,0:28:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM1號機做為Full Burnern復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木再次站在它的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.80,0:28:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此而振奮不已的妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運沒有停止對人們的磨練
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妮娜、凱利、浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.33,0:28:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏繞著的繩索沒有絲毫鬆動
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.23,0:28:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.95,0:28:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月面上的攻防戰即將拉開序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.94,0:28:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}藍耀的火焰中
